WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:06.800
Haoran

2
00:00:10.733 --> 00:00:12.666
We're really gone.

3
00:00:12.966 --> 00:00:16.066
We haven't had time to say two words

4
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:18.166
It's really mother-son love

5
00:00:18.166 --> 00:00:21.200
Do you think I'll soften my heart by pretending like this?

6
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:22.100
Your Highness the Lion

7
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:23.566
Haoran and the others are not rebels

8
00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:24.933
He has just been restored

9
00:00:24.933 --> 00:00:26.600
How could it be possible to do such a thing as rebellion?

10
00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:28.166
Please let him go

11
00:00:28.166 --> 00:00:29.766
Let him go

12
00:00:29.766 --> 00:00:32.800
I see you are also a little bit attractive

13
00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.500
Kneel down and I can spare his life

14
00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:41.800
Freeze

